parameters: (I wonder what she wants to convey.)

Ronoa, you know... She said, I'm glad to see you after such a
long time.

It seems like Lunaroa really likes this village... The village
chief is also kind.

I might understand Lunaroa's feelings a little. Maybe because
it's a little similar to Hatayaki Village.

This is an air raid shelter that was built during the war... It's
an old one, but it should still be usable.

\SE[2]...Laura, take the children and go ahead. \!\SE[3]I will
proceed while keeping an eye on the rear.

Lady Vega... I have a request for you. I apologize for burdening
you with this...
